Kristin Schafer with Sarah Blust, Brian Lipsett, Penny Newman and Richard Wiles 
(Public Interest Publications, P.O. Box 229, Arlington, Va.: $17, plus $2 
postage; 157 pp., illustrated, paperback original). As the title suggests, 
"Easy Recycling" offers basic instructions on how to prepare material to be 
