</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Bravo to "A Family United" (Feb. 9). Thank you for taking the time to show us 
what family values really mean: sticking by and supporting all the members of 
your family. 
</P>
<P>
 The Henigans deserve a standing ovation. Not just for their unconditional 
love, support and acceptance of their gay son, Patrick, but for taking an 
active, open role in making their community safer and supportive for other gay 
and lesbian teens. 
</P>
<P>
 In response to the students who protested the inclusion of the Fountain Valley 
High School Student Alliance: Your school won't have a reputation as being a 
