<TEXT>
<P>
 * The Orange County Republican Majority Coalition fully supports the Times 
editorial ("It's Time to Stop the Witch Hunts," Feb. 20) asking state Sen. John 
Lewis (R-Orange) to work more diligently on county business and less on 
personal political battles. John Lewis' behavior is an embarrassment to all 
Orange County Republicans. Lewis' "ideological cleansing" -- purging mainstream 
voices from the party -- is indicative of an agenda pursued by Orange County's 
GOP leadership. 
</P>
