it is no wonder the normally strong Orange County Republican vote has split in 
recent elections. The county's GOP leadership needs to distance itself from the 
vindictive, shallow and embarrassing behavior of politicians like Lewis. If 
not, the Democratic Party will be headed for even more election day victories. 
