<P>
GIRLS' TRACK AND FIELD / 1994 PREVIEW; ESPERANZA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Coach: Al Britt (14th year). 
</P>
<P>
 1992-93: Orange County champion, won 18th league title in school's 22-year 
history last season by taking the Empire championship in 1992, Southern Section 
Division II runner-up. 
</P>
<P>
