LH; Kristy Kierulff, Jr., HJ, LJ; Kelly O'Connor, Jr., LJ, TJ; Heather Perrin, 
So., 400; Courtney Pugmire, Jr., 800, 300 LH; Jenny Titus, Jr., 1600. 
