 Antelope Valley 104, Pasadena 82 -- Guard Danny Prince scored 27 points for 
Antelope Valley in a first-round Southern Regional playoff game. Prince hit 
seven of 15 three-point attempts as the host Marauders led, 55-42, at the half 
and never looked back. Orville Turner contributed 20 points for Antelope Valley 
(20-11). WOMEN 
