<TEXT>
<P>
 Five area wrestlers advanced to this week's State finals in Stockton by 
placing among the top eight finishers in the Southern Section Masters 
competition Saturday at Fountain Valley High. 
</P>
<P>
 James Castaneda of Alemany and Tim Bonebright of Thousand Oaks placed second 
in their weight divisions, Agoura's Chad Payne and Rio Mesa's Tom Nelford 
finished third and heavyweight Sean Burdick of Ventura was sixth. 
</P>
<P>
