<HEADLINE>
<P>
CLINTON TO MEET GEORGIA'S SHEVARDNADZE ON MARCH 7 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 President Clinton will meet Georgia President Eduard Shevardnadze for the 
first time on March 7 at the White House, the Administration announced Friday. 
</P>
<P>
 Shevardnadze, former Soviet foreign minister, will be making an official visit 
to the United States March 6-8. 
</P>
</TEXT>
