By Reuter 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Forty illegal immigrants, most of them from India, were found hidden in a 
sewer in Mexico's western state of Guerrero apparently waiting to be picked up 
by smugglers and transported into the United States, the attorney general's 
office said Friday. 
</P>
