succeeds Robert J. Gardner, who was appointed president of Abbey's 
majority-owned subsidiary, Abbey Pharmaceutical Services Inc., last August. 
Before joining the company, Hartnett was vice president of operations for 
Homedco Group Inc. He has also been vice president, chief operating officer and 
chief financial officer at the Doheny Eye Institute in Los Angeles, and held 
finance and operations positions at Western Carloading Co. and Gulf & Western 
Industries, now Paramount Communications, in New York. 
