<TEXT>
<P>
 Australia -- Marcia Harlan, Encinitas: "Pensione Sydney, 25-27 Georgina St., 
Newtown NSW 2042 (011- 61-2-550-1700). Our hosts, Ron and Jill, were 
delightful.They picked us up at the airport, gave us a short tour and 
recommended several restaurants. Our room had a great view -- we will 
definitely go back." Rates: About $82-$98 per night. 
</P>
<P>
 California -- Harriet Bilder, Idyllwild: "The Arenas Inn, 680 W. Arenas Road, 
Palm Springs 92262; (619) 325-0551. A small, immaculately kept apartment-hotel 
with one or two bedrooms, full kitchens. Within easy walk of downtown." Rates: 
$95-$165 per night. 
</P>
<P>
 Ireland -- Tom Bogosian, Claremont: "Cnoc Mhuire (Hill of Mary), Castle Road, 
Kilkenny, 011-353- 56-62161. A lovely B&B with excellent location and a very 
cordial owner." Rates: About $20 per person per night. 
</P>
<P>
 Send recommendations to Travel Section, The Times, Times Mirror Square, Los 
Angeles 90053.  
