<HEADLINE>
<P>
'WOLVES NEED YOU' 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Thank you for acknowledging the sad story of wolves in Alaska ("Howling 
Controversy Over Wolf-Killing," Feb. 6). 
</P>
<P>
 Those of us who love wolves hope that other Americans will realize that Gov. 
Hickel is destroying a magnificent resource that belongs to all Americans, not 
simply greedy hunters looking for easy kills! 
</P>
<P>
 We urge all travelers to become involved and informed on this issue. The 
wolves need you. Help save them before they are cruelly decimated. 
</P>
<P>
 CHRISTINA KAY 
</P>
<P>
 Malibu 
</P>
<P>
 * 
</P>
<P>
 Much to my amazement, your section highlighted Alaska. In view of the horrific 
slaughter of wolves, you certainly could have chosen a far better article. 
Alaska should be boycotted for the continuous wanton slaughter of animals. 
</P>
<P>
 JOAN RICHARDSON 
</P>
<P>
 San Clemente 
</P>
